    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/3e42d660977959d2269bbb5a2e196330.avif?t=1731403314\" width=616 height=134 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/1ebf881c304833ab1f4cc6d53e1ca9d4.poster.avif?t=1731403314\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/1ebf881c304833ab1f4cc6d53e1ca9d4.webm?t=1731403314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/1ebf881c304833ab1f4cc6d53e1ca9d4.mp4?t=1731403314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款可爱休闲的益智游戏，规则简单，无需复杂的玩法——享受放松的游戏体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用卡牌在地图上构建各种形状的方块，填满整个区域即可获胜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/a620fca8eef2b7933752d68f5d8ec1c3.avif?t=1731403314\" width=616 height=134 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/110548efecdff0b821b2f0b67113b26e.poster.avif?t=1731403314\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/110548efecdff0b821b2f0b67113b26e.webm?t=1731403314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/110548efecdff0b821b2f0b67113b26e.mp4?t=1731403314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇到困难了吗？使用能力卡牌来扭转局势！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/47e582af25f0ae1b62a866e89be518c1.poster.avif?t=1731403314\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/47e582af25f0ae1b62a866e89be518c1.webm?t=1731403314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/47e582af25f0ae1b62a866e89be518c1.mp4?t=1731403314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受120个精心制作的关卡，让你的创造力引导你解决它们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都有无数种解答，释放你的想象力来通关！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/8a4022465d03e1238bbb3963cadf967a.avif?t=1731403314\" width=616 height=126 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/899acd229d8ae9af154eb8f81c0b3165.poster.avif?t=1731403314\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/899acd229d8ae9af154eb8f81c0b3165.webm?t=1731403314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201880/extras/899acd229d8ae9af154eb8f81c0b3165.mp4?t=1731403314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>新功能：每日谜题！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天推出一个全新、精心手工打造的谜题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来挑战自己，激发你的思维！</p>",
